letting prd be
    [(0, 0),   $ task 1 has no predecessor (use 0 as sentinel)
     (1, 2),   $ task 2 starts >= 2 after task 1 finishes
     (1, 1),   $ task 3 starts >= 1 after task 1 finishes
     (2, 0),   $ task 4 starts >= 0 after task 2 finishes
     (3, 1)]   $ task 5 starts >= 1 after task 3 finishes

